61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">$name = new $class_name(); //发生致命错误</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">?&gt;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);"><br style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">2. 不会认为是限定名称</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">PHP在编译脚本的时候就确定了元素所在的空间，以及导入的情况。而在解析脚本时字符串形式调用只能认为是非限定名称和完全限定名称，而永远不可能是限定名称。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">复制代码 代码如下:</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);"><br style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">&lt;?php</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">namespace Blog;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">//导入Common类</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">use BlogArticleCommon;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">//我想使用非限定名称调用BlogArticleCommon</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">$common_class_name = &#39;Common&#39;;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">//实际会被当作非限定名称，也就表示当前空间的Common类，但我当前类没有创建Common类</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">$common = new $common_class_name(); //发生致命错误：Common类不存在</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">//我想使用限定名称调用BlogArticleCommon</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">$common_class_name = &#39;ArticleCommon&#39;;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">//实际会被当作完全限定名称，也就表示Article空间下的Common类，但我下面只定义了BlogArticle空间而不是Article空间</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">$common = new $common_class_name(); //发生致命错误：ArticleCommon类不存在</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);"><br style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">namespace BlogArticle;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">class Common { }</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">?&gt;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);"><br style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">总结</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &quot;Pingfang SC&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">我对PHP的命名空间刚刚接触，也不能随便给一些没有实践的建议。我个人认为命名空间的作用和功能都很强大，如果要写插件或者通用库的时候再也不用担心重名问题。不过如果项目进行到一定程度，要通过增加命名空间去解决重名问题，我觉得工作量不会比重构名字少。也不得不承认它的语法会对项目增加一定的复杂度，因此从项目一开始的时候就应该很好的规划它，并制定一个命名规范。</p><p><br/></p>','秦林慧','2016-09-21 20:10:19','7','7','./Public/Uploads/2016-09-21/57e278abd126d.jpg');
