values('35',' 格式化时间戳，时间加一天',' 格式化时间戳，时间加一天','<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.csdn.net/fgdfgasd/article/details/42004703" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 30px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 36px;"><span style="font-size: 36px;">格式化时间戳，时间加一天</span></a></p><p><a href="http://blog.csdn.net/fgdfgasd/article/details/42004703" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 30px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 36px;"><span style="font-size: 36px;"><br/></span></a></p><p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Console, Verdana, &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 14px; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">版权声明：本文为博主原创文章，未经博主允许不得转载。</span><br/></p><p>$ceshi=&quot;1417247764&quot;; &nbsp;//时间戳格式</p><p>第一种：</p><p>$ceshi+86400;//在时间戳的基础上加一天(即60*60*24)<br/></p><p>第二种：</p><p>$firstdaystr=date(&quot;Y-m-d H:i:s&quot;,$ceshi); //格式化时间戳，转为正常格式 2014-12-18<br/></p><p>//$end_time=strtotime($firstdaystr.&quot; +24 hours&quot;); //把时间加24小时，就是加一天。并且是时间戳的格式</p><p>$end_time=date(&quot;Y-m-d H:i&quot;,strtotime($firstdaystr.&quot; +24 hours&quot;)); &nbsp;//时间加一天，时间转为正常格式<br/></p><p><br/></p><p>一些例子：</p><pre id="best-content-353267895" class="best-text mb-10" name="code" style="white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, 宋体, monospace; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(241, 254, 221);">date(&#39;Y-m-d&nbsp;H:i:s&#39;,strtotime(&#39;+1&nbsp;day&#39;));</pre><pre id="best-content-353267895" class="best-text mb-10" name="code" style="white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, 宋体, monospace; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(241, 254, 221);">date(&#39;Y-m-d&nbsp;H:i:s&#39;,strtotime(&quot;+1&nbsp;day&nbsp;+1&nbsp;hour&nbsp;+1&nbsp;minute&quot;);</pre><pre id="answer-content-353229896" class="answer-text mb-10" name="code" style="white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, 宋体, monospace; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">可以修改参数1为任何想需要的数&nbsp;&nbsp;day也可以改成year（年），month（月），hour（小时），minute（分），second（秒）</pre><pre id="answer-content-353229896" class="answer-text mb-10" name="code" style="white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, 宋体, monospace; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">$tomorrow&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;date(&quot;Y-m-d&quot;,mktime&nbsp;(0,0,0,date(&quot;m&quot;)&nbsp;&nbsp;,date(&quot;d&quot;)+1,date(&quot;Y&quot;)));</pre><pre style="white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; border: 1px dotted rgb(119, 136, 85); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; width: 685px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);">&lt;?php
echo(strtotime(&quot;now&quot;));
echo(strtotime(&quot;3&nbsp;October&nbsp;2005&quot;));
echo(strtotime(&quot;+5&nbsp;hours&quot;));
echo(strtotime(&quot;+1&nbsp;week&quot;));
echo(strtotime(&quot;+1&nbsp;week&nbsp;3&nbsp;days&nbsp;7&nbsp;hours&nbsp;5&nbsp;seconds&quot;));
echo(strtotime(&quot;next&nbsp;Monday&quot;));
echo(strtotime(&quot;last&nbsp;Sunday&quot;));
