values('27','js如何实现发送短信验证码','js如何实现发送短信验证码，并开始倒计时，60秒内不得重发','<h1 class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 34px; line-height: 42px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">js如何实现发送短信验证码，并开始倒计时，60秒内不得重发</h1><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit;">相信做web开发的同学们一定都遇到过手机验证的问题，本文就是简单的介绍如何实现，如果你是web开发的老司机，请忽略此文吧。本文主要针对那些不太了解这方面知识的初级开发人员，下面开始详细说明。</span><br/></p><blockquote style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 12px 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none; position: relative; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">整个流程</p></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">说是js发送验证码，其实真正实现发送短信功能的还是在服务器，js不过是触发发送功能。大致流程如下：<br/></p><ol class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="margin-top: 1em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: outside;"><li><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">客户端js通过发送http请求（发短信接口）到服务器，将手机号等信息传递给服务器</p></li><li><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">服务器收到请求后校验参数，参数正确调用第三方短信接口，并将随机产生的验证码保存在服务器（通常是数据库或者缓存），参数错误，将错误信息返回给客户端</p></li><li><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">客户端收到服务器的返回，如果调用成功，开始倒计时同时等待用户输入收到的验证码，如果调用失败，将失败信息提示给用户。</p></li><li><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">用户输入验证码后，将验证码和手机号等信息发送到服务器校验</p></li><li><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">服务器收到校验请求后，对手机号和验证码用验证，将结果返回给客户端</p></li><li><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">客户端收到验证结果后，提示用户或者开始其他业务</p></li></ol><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">简单的页面：</p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><img src="http://p3.pstatp.com/large/c1300003d1edf1ea427" img_width="1004" img_height="534" alt="js如何实现发送短信验证码，并开始倒计时，60秒内不得重发" style="margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; display: block;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">发送按钮的方法</p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><img src="http://p3.pstatp.com/large/bda0004e4bd9f7ba9a9" img_width="1220" img_height="790" alt="js如何实现发送短信验证码，并开始倒计时，60秒内不得重发" style="margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; display: block;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">倒计时方法</p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><img src="http://p3.pstatp.com/large/bd90004e7b86bd9e730" img_width="1148" img_height="516" alt="js如何实现发送短信验证码，并开始倒计时，60秒内不得重发" style="margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; display: block;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">验证验证码方法</p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><img src="http://p1.pstatp.com/large/bdc0004e5ac298b7b97" img_width="1016" img_height="752" alt="js如何实现发送短信验证码，并开始倒计时，60秒内不得重发" style="margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; display: block;"/></p><p><br/></p>','秦林慧','2016-08-13 13:31:03','7','2','./Public/Uploads/2016-08-13/57aeb0978ef3b.jpg');
