on &nbsp;= json_encode($ob);</strong></span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-FAMILY: 微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; COLOR: #595959">此时$json变量的值如下：</span></p><p><img title="PHP将XML转换为数组" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160809/1470700513294206.gif"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 18px; FONT-FAMILY: 微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; COLOR: #595959">4、解析JSON字符串 
